个不受任何限制的景观，则有一个单独的模式。</p><p><strong>购买对象</strong>： <a data-i13n="cpos:21;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Nintendo;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=21fc7c82-c5eb-49a9-b5d3-fc32a78290de&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Nintendo&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiIyMWZjN2M4Mi1jNWViLTQ5YTktYjVkMy1mYzMyYTc4MjkwZGUiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cubmludGVuZG8uY29tL3N0b3JlL3Byb2R1Y3RzL2RvcmZyb21hbnRpay1zd2l0Y2gvIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiJkMmM4YjFjYi0zODRlLTQ3NjUtODQ3ZC04MjdmZDU0N2VlMjYifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAXNWdj-vCW6lozA7iDPhUYR_YP39jKq9DcjbNZ2N3ohM&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nintendo.com%2Fstore%2Fproducts%2Fdorfromantik-switch%2F">交换机</a>、 <a data-i13n="cpos:22;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:GOG.com;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=a3926e63-4324-467b-872c-52d2bfe9bd34&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=GOG.com&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiJhMzkyNmU2My00MzI0LTQ2N2ItODcyYy01MmQyYmZlOWJkMzQiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuZ29nLmNvbS9lbi9nYW1lL2RvcmZyb21hbnRpayIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiZDJjOGIxY2ItMzg0ZS00NzY1LTg0N2QtODI3ZmQ1NDdlZTI2In0&amp;signature=AQAAAXCI4wIde9lRRWYp1e0kr-wKatfdEzV6wuqQKdptoJHE&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gog.com%2Fen%2Fgame%2Fdorfromantik">PC</a></p><h2><em>短途远足</em></h2><p><core-commerce id="7640d5bd654b4938a5238b8e328e24e8" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:23;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:GOG.com;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=a3926e63-4324-467b-872c-52d2bfe9bd34&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=GOG.com&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiJhMzkyNmU2My00MzI0LTQ2N2ItODcyYy01MmQyYmZlOWJkMzQiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuZ29nLmNvbS9lbi9nYW1lL2Ffc