 simulation game.</p><p> <strong>Buy for</strong> : <a data-i13n="cpos:43;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Humble Bundle;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=8cce7f0e-1975-4189-ad0c-2981dc30d13c&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Humble+Bundle&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI4Y2NlN2YwZS0xOTc1LTQxODktYWQwYy0yOTgxZGMzMGQxM2MiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuaHVtYmxlYnVuZGxlLmNvbS9zdG9yZS9ldXJvLXRydWNrLXNpbXVsYXRvci0yIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiJkMmM4YjFjYi0zODRlLTQ3NjUtODQ3ZC04MjdmZDU0N2VlMjYifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAcrYTkeMy2BAvBL24z1g6u8ha7MdWAduO4PGUqxw-h_p&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.humblebundle.com%2Fstore%2Feuro-truck-simulator-2">PC</a><br> <strong>Length</strong> : <a data-i13n="cpos:44;pos:1" href="https://howlongtobeat.com/game/3199">117 hours</a></p><h2> <em>Wide Ocean Big Jacket</em> </h2><p><core-commerce id="102828c5ecee4cfabf86d1030cc43023" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> There&#39;s been no shortage of easy-to-play “walking simulators” in recent years, but <a data-i13n="cpos:45;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Humble Bundle;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=8cce7f0e-1975-4189-ad0c-2981dc30d13c&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Humble+Bundle&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI4Y2NlN2YwZS0xOTc1LTQxODktYWQwYy0yOTgxZGMzMGQxM2MiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuaHVtYmxlYnVuZGxlLmNvbS9zdG9yZS93aWRlLW9jZWFuLWJpZy1qYWNrZXQiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6ImQyYzhiMWNiLTM4NGUtNDc2NS04NDdkLTgyN2ZkNTQ3ZWUyNiJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAcwETJEl471KX1MGHffNZn2FrubK86O3rpZlbnVO_qoA&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.humblebundle.com%2Fstore%2Fwide-ocean-big-jacket"><em>Wide Ocean Big Jacket</em></a> stands out among them for telling a particularly warm short story. It&#39;s crudely animated and maybe an hour long, but it develops more identifiable and <em>human</em> characters in that time than most big-budget games do in 30 hours of gameplay.</p><p> The story follows the camping trip of a young couple, Brad and Cloanne, their 13-year-old niece Mord and her friend Ben, and the subsequent lessons they learn about love and each other. It has the air of an indie comedy: a little quirky, funny but not mean-spirited, honest but not long-winded, and moving when it&#39;s time to bring the story home. Its world isn&#39;t ending, and there&#39;s no combat. It&#39;s a game about <em>these</em> characters in <em>this</em> specific moment, and it&#39;s presented like a series of memories, something its bold colors amplify.</p><p> The game&#39;s approach to interactivity plays a big role in selling all of this. Instead of merely controlling a specific character, you&#39;re often in charge of the camera, a sort of director role that brings you closer to each scene but distances you, the player, from the action (or what qualifies as action in this case).</p><p> <strong>Buy for</strong> : <a data-i13n="cpos:46;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Nintendo;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=21fc7c82-c5eb-49a9-b5d3-fc32a78290de&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Nintendo&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAVD5zevdP8ciReCydP3Rj7IIV8GwSPRQss3tp-2YXHwP&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nintendo.com%2Fstore%2Fproducts%2Fwide-ocean-big-jacket-switch%2F">Switch</a> , <a data-i13n="cpos:47;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Humble Bundle;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=8cce7f0e-1975-4189-ad0c-2981dc30d13c&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Humble+Bundle&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI4Y2NlN2YwZS0xOTc1LTQxODktYWQwYy0yOTgxZGMzMGQxM2MiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuaHVtYmxlYnVuZGxlLmNvbS9zdG9yZS93aWRlLW9jZWFuLWJpZy1qYWNrZXQiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6ImQyYz